data.name: Sawa Okita/沖田 紗羽 (Tari Tari) LoRA | 3 Outfits
data.description:
I have a form for requests; check it out if you want to request a character.

Sawa Okita from Tari Tari. Trained on NAI. Tested at 0.8-1.0 strength.

Trigger word is "okitasawa" and "low twintails" is required.

  • Add "hat, choker, frilled dress, black skirt, bare shoulders" for her regular appearance.

  • Add "brown jacket, red necktie, yellow sweater vest, blue skirt, pantyhose" for her school uniform.

  • Add "white shirt, short sleeves, red necktie, blue skirt" for her alternate school uniform.

A request from the form. Check out my Discord if you want to chat about video games (or yell at me about requests.)
